LOVE KNOCKING
Love, Love, Love,
A loving heart calling.
A loving heart inspired.
A loving heart filled with hopes.
Love, Love, Love.
Sharing, Tasting, Smelling,
Loving all, Loving Life.
Love strengthening the soul,
The soul enlightening the heart,
The heart inspiring the body,
Pumping Love, Loving to pump.
Oh Love, Come on in,
Welcome home,
This is your heart,
Spread all around,
state of love.

